This is dynamic programming algorithm to solve the all-pairs shortest paths problem.
Recurrence A[i,j,k] = min{A[i,j,k-1], A[i,k,k-1] + A[k,j,k-1]}


```scala
for {

   k <- 1 to n

   i <- 1 to n

   j <- 1 to n

} {

   A(i)(j)(k) = math.min(A(i)(j)(k-1), A(i)(k)(k-1) + A(k)(j)(k-1))

}
```
